  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/50ebc95a1cdc7c3e2dcae3accdc61369.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=178 /></span><strong>WEBFISHING</strong> is a multiplayer online casual fishing game where you relax, hang out, make friends, and catch fish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CATCH THEM ALL!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nearly <strong>100 </strong>different creatures to catch- from the smallest snail to the biggest shark- you can catch it! Complete your journal, find rare fish, get loads of money, and get tons of special rewards! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.webm?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.mp4?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE AND CUSTOMIZE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the ultimate fisherman! Upgrade your gear with new baits, lures, and rods- and collect tons of different cosmetics and props to show off your personality!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/50ca2a369a239df19b172a876346d119.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/50ca2a369a239df19b172a876346d119.webm?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH FRIENDS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WEBFISHING is designed around being social and hanging out with friends and strangers in the camp! Meet new people, find hidden spots, make awful fish puns, and catch fish together!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/8ec78c8aa38d0349e99fbbc7c6a588f0.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/8ec78c8aa38d0349e99fbbc7c6a588f0.webm?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/8ec78c8aa38d0349e99fbbc7c6a588f0.mp4?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY WITH TOYS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play REAL Guitar! Punch your friends! Draw with chalk! There's many tools and toys to play with in the sandbox of WEBFISHING!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/7f0bdd8cc44b087d0222e42a31536cec.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/7f0bdd8cc44b087d0222e42a31536cec.webm?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/7f0bdd8cc44b087d0222e42a31536cec.mp4?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/50ebc95a1cdc7c3e2dcae3accdc61369.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=178 /></span><strong>WEBFISHING</strong> is a multiplayer online casual fishing game where you relax, hang out, make friends, and catch fish!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CATCH THEM ALL!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nearly <strong>100 </strong>different creatures to catch- from the smallest snail to the biggest shark- you can catch it! Complete your journal, find rare fish, get loads of money, and get tons of special rewards! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.webm?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/ceeb7ffe73a474edac32fb43ef05d33c.mp4?t=1728673229\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE AND CUSTOMIZE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the ultimate fisherman! Upgrade your gear with new baits, lures, and rods- and collect tons of different cosmetics and props to show off your personality!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146520/extras/50ca2a369a239df19b172a876346d119.poster.avif?t=1728673229\" width=55